}
```

### Useful Queries

```javascript
// Find all documents for a specific client (across all matters)
const clientDocs = await db
  .collection('teams').doc(teamId)
  .collection('documents')
  .where('clientIds', 'array-contains', clientId)
  .orderBy('loggedAt', 'desc')
  .get()

