### Error Recovery Strategies

```javascript
// Upload retry logic
let retryCount = 0;
const maxRetries = 3;

while (retryCount < maxRetries) {
  try {
    await uploadFile(file);
    break; // Success
  } catch (error) {
    retryCount++;
    await delay(Math.pow(2, retryCount) * 1000); // Exponential backoff
  }
}
```

